But give me leave, as a Friend to such that were dear to her, (and whither to me let GOD be Witn
                  •••
               ) to entreat, and beseech, and adjure you all to Pray for yourselves, and for one another, as she did; and it may strengthen your Faith and Hope, that she has laid up such a Stock of Prayers for you, which have been long entrusted with the common Advocate.
